PDF Writer
5/30/2002

is now part of the print_kit of the OBOS (OpenBeOS) project.
http://open-beos.sourceforge.net

Developers: 
  Name              Email address                Native language
  Phillipe Houdoin  <philippe.houdoin@free.fr>   French
